# Tests (hashicorp-vault-clm-discovery)

When you add or change Go behavior:

1. Add or update tests in the same change (`internal/**`).
2. Run `go test ./...` before considering work done.
3. For scanner/cert parsing, use table tests and local TLS fixtures where practical.

Docs-only changes do not require tests.

Org SDLC: verify with `go test ./...` and `go build ./...` before PR. Docker: `docker compose -f deploy/docker-compose.yml build`.
